title: I Am Han Sanqian
description: I Am Han Sanqian Han Sanqian has been in Zuo Su’s family for three years and was called the trash son-in-law because of his relatives. In order to prevent his wife Su Yingxia from being humiliated by others, Han Sanqian worked secretly to become a super son-in-law and began preparing for payback. Han Sanqian I Am Han Sanqian Wo Shi Han Sanqian 我是韩三千
